rating_comment: Yaksha is like my second home. Every stay at Yaksha is not just affordable but very comfortable and pleasant .Snom ensures that the guests are taken care of properly and She is a fabulous host!
It was my 4th or 5th visit. Good place to stay.
We were so thankful for the great communication and amazing hospitality. We felt like we were coming home. We were provided for and taken care of. We are very thankful!

Everything about Yaksha is a delight - the host, the space, the hospitality and amenities. We are yet to sample their food yet but there's always a next time and I'm sure that'll be stellar too! We are extremely happy to have found this gem of a place in Siliguri.
Thank you Snom & staff for your wonderful service! We'll definitely keep coming back for more x
